cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper presents a machine learning approach for data association in multi-target localization, which involves pattern recognition and clustering. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which suggests a possible fit with cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
